{"tid":2250259,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港酒店討論(7) - 住酒店要有一套","createTime":"2020-10-20T03:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T07:22:54.000Z","uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b899da2d46bd394b93f9ec853e57966c5e74b8e","tid":2250259,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"各大酒店嘅staycation package 變幻莫測 各類債券層出不窮<br />\n要問問題嘅自己做咗功課先<br />\n記得留低<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>BUDGET</strong></span></span>同埋要求<br />\n呢度啲巴打會盡力幫你<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"large\"><ins>酒店心水推介-update(排名不分先後)</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">維港海景</span></strong><br />\n灣仔: Renaissance Harbour View / Grand Hyatt<br />\n金鐘: Conrad/ Island Shangri-La/ JW Marriott<br />\n中環: MO／ Four Seasons<br />\n尖沙咀: Peninsula/ Rosewood/ K11 Artus/ Sheraton<br />\n尖東/紅磡: Kowloon Shangri-La/ 海景嘉福洲際/ Hotel ICON / 千禧新世界／Kerry<br />\n九龍站: Ritz Carlton/ W HongKong<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">價廉物美包泳池</span></strong><br />\n北角: Hyatt Centric Victoria Harbour (<span class=\"red\"><strong>人滿為患</strong></span>)<br />\n佐敦: Eaton HK<br />\n沙田: 帝逸酒店/ Courtyard Shatin<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">注意事項</span></span><br />\n1.酒店設施(包括健身室,泳池,及行政酒廊)的開放時間<br />\n或會因應香港特區政府所制定的防疫措施而有所更改<br />\n建議入住前可以先向酒店查詢及確認<br />\n<br />\n2.接受在《預防及控制疾病（規管跨境交通工具及到港者）規例》（第 599H 章）下 由指定地區抵港人士預訂房間的酒店列表:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/inbound/hotels.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Finbound%2Fhotels.pdf&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=f2ce927a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/inbound/hotels.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"80b2f31fa675db651d1b27acb1be898c00c7aaf7","tid":2250259,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"萬豪半價卷10/19後情況：<b